{"tid":369140,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣 懷才不遇?","createTime":"2017-08-22T05:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T09:16:34.000Z","uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"343a4e5289d26fa6df219cc0cf281f7d148c39f0","tid":369140,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"自問自己有<br />\n拿破倫既謀略<br />\n希特拉既演說技巧<br />\n李嘉誠既長遠目光<br />\n又不失<br />\n柳永既放盪同風流<br />\n當年睇相佬話我 一係就成為金輪聖王 一係就可以好似佛陀咁教化眾生<br />\n點解我依加仲要係連登開膠POST咁撚可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39a961cc9347eb22b839e4e46b8efbdd62aa6ad","tid":369140,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"生不逢時牙清<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f34a9d092ad28c2b3b4a3e0a831bd398c1eacd3","tid":369140,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:35:13.000Z","msg":"清依家做緊m記？"},{"pid":"7642a0d0f159ba9c8eab883c2e26e36231c6e2ef","tid":369140,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:35:48.000Z","msg":"咪學下衲dee不時上去幫d失足婦女開光囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有飲酒食狗肉打老婆<br />\n酒肉穿腸過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb44e4a4133e9843e61b041e4be45a84728f55c5","tid":369140,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清依家做緊m記？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f595a667cc9c80f64759c8754b2f2393453f2de0","tid":369140,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"}]}